      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIVERLAND SON (1) has a strong record this trip with 11 wins and five placings from 18 starts. Scored by 4 lengths last time (19.78) in a Grade 4/5 over 350m at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. BULL MUNDY (8) stuck on well last time to finish 2 lengths back in third (28.10) at Casino in a Grade 5 over 484m. The form out of last race has been strong. Expected to be in the finish again. GOAL KICKER (4) missed the frame last time but before three back recorded the quickest win (19.90) on the program at this track in a Grade 5. Can feature with the right run. REEL 'EM MINI (2) was well fancied last time on the strength of a win two back but could only manage eighth (17.70) at Casino.",
